sec.p:
Until now eighty-two species of Cochylini from twelve
           genera have been recorded from Iran and these are the following:
              Aethes Billberg, 1820;
              Agapeta Huebner , 1822;
              Ceratoxanthis Razowski, 1960;
              Cochylidia Obraztsov, 1956;
              Cochylimorpha Razowski, 1960;
              Cochylis Treitschke, 1829;
              Diceratura Djakonov, 1929;
              Eugnosta Huebner , 1825;
              Fulvoclysia Obraztsov, 1943;
              Gynnidomorpha Turner, 1916;
              Phalonidia Le Marchand, 1933 and
              Phtheochroa Stephens, 1829 ( ).
